n- The problem is at layer 1/2 on pc_0_1 (interface DOWN / neighbor resolution failing). There is no evidence of BGP or routing-table errors contributing to this outage for 10.0.1.0/24.", "generation_info": {"finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 13468, "output_tokens": 1920, "total_tokens": 15388, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 12928}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 832}}}
